1981;;Gas;;Canadian;;Les Rose;;Philip Akin, Susan Anspach;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gas_(1981_film);;A small Midwestern town is thrown into chaos when the local oil tycoon Duke Stuyvesant orchestrates a phony oil shortage in order to increase profits. News reporter Jane Beardsley tries to uncover the plot. Radio DJ Nick the Noz, observing from his station's news helicopter, reports on the craziness caused by the gasoline shortage.